OL,3,CRats on the rise after wet weather
OL,5,FRat activity across the UK has
OL,6,Fincreased significantly over the past
OL,7,Fyear, with Yorkshire experiencing one
OL,8,Fof the sharpest regional rises.
OL,10,FRentokil Pest Control said it had
OL,11,Frecorded a 10% year-on-year increase
OL,12,Fin confirmed rodent activity, but
OL,13,Fregionally Yorkshire recorded a 20%
OL,14,Fspike.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland recorded the largest
OL,17,Fincrease of 26%, and several other
OL,18,Fregions, including the West Midlands
OL,19,F(16%) and Scotland (14%), also had
OL,20,Fdouble-digit rises.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
