OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772471476
OL,3,CRats on the rise after wet weather
OL,5,FThe increase is thought to be due to
OL,6,F2025 being the UK's warmest year on
OL,7,Frecord and then exacerbated by recent
OL,8,Fwet weather, with England getting 35%
OL,9,Fmore rainfall than usual.
OL,11,FRentokil explained that milder weather
OL,12,Fcould increase rat reproduction by
OL,13,Fextending their breeding season and
OL,14,Fleading to larger populations.
OL,16,FSustained heavy rain can also flood
OL,17,Fburrow systems and drainage networks,
OL,18,Fdisplacing rats and increasing the
OL,19,Flikelihood of infestations as they
OL,20,Fseek higher, drier shelter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
